                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header" role="tab" id="heading38">
                                        <p class="mb-0">
                                            <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse38"
                                                aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseseven">
                                                Factsheet - May 2014
                                            </a>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapse38" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                                        data-parent="#accordion">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            In the month of May we have added a few core positions to our portfolio.
                                            Google (Class C Shares) & ICICI Bank Ltd. Navneet Education remains a small
                                            position & we’re participating in the United Spirits Special
                                            Situation.<br /><br />

                                            The top 10 equity holdings comprise of 53% of the portfolio. As of 30th May,
                                            71.56% of our portfolio is invested in Indian Equities & 20.66% is invested
                                            in Foreign Equities with the balance amount in Cash Equivalents (including
                                            CBLO).<br /><br />

                                            <a href="http://www.amc.ppfas.com/schemes/disclosure-of-insider-holdings/index.php"
                                                target="_blank">Click here</a> if you desire to view the PPFCP unit
                                            holdings of the directors, employees etc. of PPFAS Mutual Fund and its
                                            Sponsor. <br /><br />

                                            <em><b>Disclaimer:</b> Past performance may or may not be sustained in the
                                                future. </em><br /><br />

                                            <a href="/downloads/factsheet/2014/may/pltvf-factsheet-may-2014.pdf"
                                                class="btn btn-outline-success" target="_blank" onclick="_gaq.push(["
                                                _trackEvent","Factsheets","May",this.href]);">Download Factsheet</a>

                                            <a href="/downloads/portfolio-disclosure/Monthly-Portfolio-May-2014.xls"
                                                class="btn btn-outline-success" target="_blank" onclick="_gaq.push(["
                                                _trackEvent","Portfolio Disclossure","Excel",this.href]);">Detailed
                                                Portfolio Disclosure</a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header" role="tab" id="heading39">
                                        <p class="mb-0">
                                            <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse39"
                                                aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseseven">
                                                Factsheet - April 2014
                                            </a>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapse39" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                                        data-parent="#accordion">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            No changes have been undertaken in our core portfolio. As at April 30, 2014,
                                            63.99 % of our corpus is in Indian stocks, 19.91 % is invested in foreign
                                            stocks / depository receipts, with the balance 16.10 % in cash equivalents
                                            (including CBLO).<br /><br />

                                            Noida Toll Bridge (6.38 %), ICRA (6.11 %) and Axis Bank (6.08 %) are our top
                                            three domestic holdings while IBM continues as our top overseas holding.
                                            'Banks' are our top sectoral holding (13.00 %). Our top 10 stock holdings
                                            comprise 51.03 % of the portfolio and the top three sectors (excluding debt
                                            instruments) viz. banks, finance and software, comprise 31.49 %.
                                            <br /><br />

                                            Our diversified approach to investing (Indian stocks, foreign stocks and
                                            debt instruments) has helped us to outperform the benchmark (Nifty 500) by a
                                            margin of over 13 percentage points. This is coupled with a relatively low
                                            standard deviation of 8.48 %.<br /><br />

                                            <a href="http://www.amc.ppfas.com/schemes/disclosure-of-insider-holdings/index.php"
                                                target="_blank">Click here</a> if you desire to view the PPFCP unit
                                            holdings of the directors, employees etc. of PPFAS Mutual Fund and its
                                            Sponsor. <br /><br />

                                            <em><b>Disclaimer:</b> Past performance may or may not be sustained in the
                                                future. </em><br /><br />

                                            <a href="/downloads/factsheet/2014/april/pltvf-factsheet-april-2014.pdf"
                                                class="btn btn-outline-success" target="_blank" onclick="_gaq.push(["
